@startuml
participant User
participant Website
participant "Flask API" as FlaskAPI
participant APIFree

User -> Website: Submit travel preferences\n(destination, dates, interests)
activate Website

Website -> FlaskAPI: POST /generate\n(prefs JSON)
activate FlaskAPI

FlaskAPI -> APIFree: POST /create-itinerary\n(prefs)
activate APIFree

APIFree --> FlaskAPI: 200 OK\n(itinerary data + image URL/base64)
deactivate APIFree

FlaskAPI --> Website: 200 OK\n(itinerary JSON + image)
deactivate FlaskAPI

Website -> Website: Render itinerary and image
Website --> User: Display generated itinerary and image
deactivate Website
@enduml